steps.description:
Keep a few things in mind before you begin:
Make sure that your idea is a well thought out idea, and that you have the skill to paint it. However, if you're not the next Picasso no worries, do something that is simpler and within your means, or use a stencil. Slates are the perfect format to stencil on. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/43/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/43/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Use a good paint brushes to ensure clean edges. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Use a better quality acrylic paint. You want to avoid paints that are clumpy or are too thin, because they don't cover that well and are hard to control. Paint brushes and paint can be purchased at your local craft store or on line. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e2/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e2/Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-Decorative-Slate-Step-9Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
